&lt;p&gt;Want to join our team as a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Demand Planner&lt;/strong&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Demand Planner&lt;/strong&gt; is responsible for maintaining an informed demand plan aligned to the company’s fiscal objectives. The role will lead cross-functional discussions with the commercial and sales teams, utilizing historical data analysis along with business intelligence to provide updated plans for their assigned categories. As part of the Supply Chain group, the Demand Planner will work alongside Supply and Sourcing counterparts, providing insight for near and long-term forecasts to inform production planning at respective factories.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Job Functions &amp;amp; Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
