&lt;li&gt;Maintain direct responsibility for Demand planning functions for a specific category.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively manage demand plan at material/SKU/DC level.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the demand plan to assure proper inventory levels of products to support the business and satisfy customer demand.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the critical analysis of inventory levels to support company goals and provide creative solutions to inventory issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Correspond with sales and category leaders to determine business decisions, line planning, timing, and new product introductions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with sales operations on market and consumer trends, POS/market inventory data, statistical projections, and historical analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly with Sourcing to assist in managing inventory flow that supports production plans for each category.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate and lead cross-functional alignment to create an optimal Inventory &amp;amp; OTB Strategy aimed to support our Operational Forecast and help hedge against volatility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate, troubleshoot, and resolve any constraints which may impact service levels (demand, inputs &amp;amp; capacity).&lt;/li&gt;
