&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;The &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Production Scheduling Associate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; will work with the Production Supervisors and the supply team to schedule, coordinate daily workload for product to flow through production, maintain on time shipping and stock levels, work with customer service for any and all sales orders that must be completed, and notify the Production Supervisor when current workload exceeds capacity. This position will also assist in cycle counting of inventory.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
